      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated mechanic, a restoration enthusiast, or as a source for parts. The engine currently suffers from significant performance issues and will likely require a complete overhaul or replacement to be roadworthy again. Externally, the body shows its age with several noticeable dents, some rust bubbling on the wheel arches, and clear coat failure on the hood and roof. The interior has seen heavy use, with tears in the upholstery and some non-functional electronics. It is being sold strictly as-is, and towing will be required upon purchase.",
