      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, offered in pristine, showroom condition. This motorcar represents the pinnacle of its class, having been preserved with fastidious attention to detail and uncompromising standards. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, affirms its status as a collector-grade example. Mechanical components have been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance, delivering a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire a benchmark-quality vehicle.",
